'''''This Is Love'''' is an album by American guitarist [[Lee Ritenour]] released in 1998, and recorded for the i.e. label.<br/>
All Music noted that Ritenour "has grown as a mature jazz artist on this album".<ref name="AllMusic review">Ginell, R [http://www.allmusic.com/album/this-is-love-mw0000039079  This Is Love AllMusic review]</ref>
The album reached #4 on ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'''s Jazz chart.

